channel.title: Tinge - lagrangian (ft. industry city sleepers & TMAR) [Techno]
channel.description:
[LISTEN HERE](https://soundcloud.com/lagrangain/tinge-ft-industry-city-sleepers-tmar)
This was a fun track made for a competition done by @lowey where we submitted unused loops and then mashed them up. I used loops submitted by myself, @iammane, and @TMAR. This sound is really different than what I normally experiment with. What do you guys think of it?
